After initializing & updating all the submodules (dont forget the submodules in the vim-folder) create symlinks:

mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim
mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim/plugs
mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim/colors
ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/init.vim ~/.config/nvim/init.vim
ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/autoload ~/.config/nvim/autoload
ln -s ~/dotfiles/smyck/smyck.vim ~/.config/nvim/colors/smyck.vim
ln -s ~/dotfiles/zshrc ~/.zshrc

Once you start the neovim editor run :PlugInstall to install plugins
